headline: Corrections & Amplifications
summary: CORRECTIONS The Environmental Protection Agency took aerial photographs of Dow Chemical’s plants in Midland, Mich., in 1978, leading the company to sue. Saturday’s obituary for Paul Oreffice incorrectly said Midland, Texas.
